        <text>new courses were developed with</text>
        <edit type="grammar" crr="" comments="">the</edit>
        <text>support provided by a number of HESP projects. Based on the experience of Western universities, the topics of linguistics, computer science, mathematics and computational linguistics were selected.</text>
